        Parameters:
        nbjour - The number of travel days
        heure_depart - The hours of the rider's begin time every morning
        heure_min_resto_midi - The earliest business hours of restaurants at noon every day
        heure_max_resto_midi - The latest business hours of restaurants at noon every day
        heure_resto_midi - The hours of the rider's lunch time at noon every day
        heure_min_resto_soir - The earliest business hours of restaurants every night
        heure_max_resto_soir - The latest business hours of restaurants every night
        heure_resto_soir - The hours of the rider's diner time every night
        heure_max_hotel - The latest business hours of the hotel every night
